      <title>诺耶称欧盟每年可筹集 2150 亿美元储蓄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/eu-could-muster-215-billion-a-year-from-savings-noyer-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行前政策制定者克里斯蒂安·诺耶表示，如果欧盟改善储蓄目标方式，那么欧盟每年可能向实体经济投入多达 2000 亿欧元（合 2150 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/eu-could-muster-215-billion-a-year-from-savings-noyer-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 09:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
